 using future orders, meaning it predicts the trend more accurately,

00:05:06.411 --> 00:05:13.520
a future trend, for your newbies audience,  is an order to 
 open a trade if the price would reach a certain limit,

00:05:13.516 --> 00:05:18.950
if the trend goes the other way, the 
 order will not be executed at all.

